<div><head>禮記音義隱</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-1a.2">古者屨頭鼻綦繩相連結之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-1a.3">將升堂解之也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-1a.4">酳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-1a.5">飯畢蕩口也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-1a.6">東海樂浪人呼容十二斛者為鼓。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-2a.2">獵車之形，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-2a.3">今之鉤車是也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-2a.4">衣車如鱉而長也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-2a.5">漢桓帝之時，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-2a.6">禁臣下乘之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-2a.7">天子曰不豫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-2a.8">諸侯曰不茲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-2a.9">大夫曰犬馬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-2a.10">士曰負薪。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-3a.2">雖無列於朝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-3a.3">有告凶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-3a.4">猶反告於宗後。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-3a.5">其都無親在故國，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-3a.6">不復來往也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-3a.7">嫌見奪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-3a.8">故云恐辱親也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-4a.2">嗇夫主諸侯所齎幣、帛、皮、圭之禮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-4a.3">奉之以白於天子也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-4a.4">雉之肥則足疏。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-4a.5">並《曲禮正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-4a.6">羨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-4a.7">車道。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-4a.8">《檀弓釋文》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-5a.2">萬物在人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-5a.3">外非巳所有。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-5a.4">故以多為貴也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-5a.5">樂多其外見者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-5a.6">謂衣服萬物，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-5a.7">悉外見物也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-5a.8">巳有功德，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-5a.9">故得使有所物，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-5a.10">以光輝祀先人為樂也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-5a.11">並《禮器正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-6a.2">腊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-6a.3">久也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-6a.4">久酒有毒。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-6a.5">《郊特牲釋文》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-6a.6">齊人以相絞訐為掉磬。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-6a.7">腱，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-6a.8">筋之大者。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-6a.9">並《內則釋文》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-7a.2">以魚須飾文竹之邊。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-7a.3">須音班。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-7a.4">《玉藻釋文》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-7a.5">尊者委四矢於地，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-7a.6">一一取以投，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-7a.7">卑者不敢委於地，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-7a.8">悉執之也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-8a.2">君怠惰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-8a.3">當張設法而助之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-8a.4">或張強其志，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-8a.5">以廣大之也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-8a.6">並《少儀正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-8a.7">侇之言移也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-8a.8">《雜記釋文》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-9a" ed="CHANT" n="001-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-9a.2">㪺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-9a.3">容四升也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-9a.4">《喪大記釋文》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-9a.5">堂廉即堂上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-9a.6">近南霤為廉也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-9a.7">練後三日一哭於次，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-9a.8">次在中門外，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-9a.9">謂堊室也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-9a.10">至大祥則不復於外。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-9a.11">若有弔者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-9a.12">則入即位哭。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-10a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-10a" ed="CHANT" n="001-10a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-10a.2">大夫、士父母之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-10a.3">既小祥而歸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-10a.4">庶子為大夫、士者也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-10a.5">適子終喪在殯宮也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-10a.6">朱綠皆繒也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-10a.7">振容在下。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-11a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-11a" ed="CHANT" n="001-11a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-11a.2">羽葆、功布等，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-11a.3">其象皆如麾。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-11a.4">並《喪大記‧正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-11a.5">卑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-11a.6">音必利反。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-11a.7">《祭統釋文》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-11a.8">符，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-11a.9">謂甘露醴泉之屬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-11a.10">長，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-11a.11">謂麟鳳五靈之屬。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-11a.12">《經解釋文》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-12a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-12a" ed="CHANT" n="001-12a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-12a.2">某甫「且」字，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-12a.3">且，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-12a.4">假借此字也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-12a.5">《曲禮疏》引《音義隱》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-12a.6">堥，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-12a.7">土釜也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-12a.8">《內則疏》引《隱義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-13a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-13a" ed="CHANT" n="001-13a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-13a.2">士有三等，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-13a.3">一等一拜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-13a.4">故三下膝也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-13a.5">一云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-13a.6">旁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-13a.7">猶不正，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-13a.8">或云眾上都共三拜也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1100_CHANT_001-13a.9">《喪大記疏》引《隱義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
